lilo-installer (1.01) unstable; urgency=low

  * Joey Hess
    - Use the user-params command to get parameters the user manually
      entered on the command line, and add these into lilo.conf.
    - Copy code from partman to convert lvm /dev/mapper/<vg>-<lv> to a form
      that lvdisplay won't choke on.
    - lilo sometimes needs proc to be mounted to access /proc/partitions.
      So make sure it's mounted before running lilo, and unmount after.
